t or Dairy Bar, at this time he told me to park the cars somewhere else. I asked the property owner if anything changed with the septic system. He said he was told to come in late one evening or on the weekend and put another septic system n without the knowledge of the health department. (This is hear say). This creates the problem I don’t understand. I am concerned that when the road comes through I will be shut down due to the fact the septic system is condemned or some other reason. I am already losing the drive through for the dairy bar and the car lot. I also don’t understand how one business is paid to relocate and the others are fine even though we all used the same septic system. I feel like my rights have been violated. I would appreciate your response to this manner. Sincerely, Richard Buchanan 145 Bear Wallow Road Burnsville, NC 28714 E-mail heavenlycool72@netzero.com Home 828-682-9517 Bus. 828-682-3052 Cell 828-284-3612

